Package spoon.support.modelobs

Class EmptyModelChangeListener

java.lang.Object
spoon.support.modelobs.EmptyModelChangeListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
FineModelChangeListener
public class EmptyModelChangeListener extends Object implements FineModelChangeListener
is the listener that creates the action on the model. This default listener does nothing.
